## Design Considerations

**Constraints:**
- Minimum column width: ~200px (to fit card content)
- Gap between columns: 16px (1rem)
- Maximum visible columns: 5

**Calculations:**
- 5 columns visible: Each column gets ~20% of viewport width (minus gaps)
- 3 columns visible: Each column gets ~33% of viewport width (minus gaps)
- 7+ columns: First 5 get ~20%, remaining require horizontal scroll

**Edge Cases:**
- Very narrow viewports (< 1200px): Consider switching to single-column or 2-column layout
- Very wide viewports (> 2560px): Columns should not exceed reasonable width (~400px)

